Problem on Ages-2 - Placement Exercise
NOTE: This kind of question is very common in campus placement ( TCS, Wipro, etc.) 
because it makes the use of basic linear equations.

Problem:
Ram is three times as old as Sam.
Two years ago, he was five times as old as Sam.
What is the present age of Ram?

